.  Binomial Theorem.  Use the Maple command  " }{TEXT 259 6 "expand" }
{TEXT 256 2 "  " }{TEXT -1 34 "to calculate the expansion of     " }
{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(a+b)^n;" "6#),&%\"aG\"\"\"%\"bGF&%\"nG" }{TEXT -1 63 "
    for values n=1..10 .  In each case use the Maple command   " }
{TEXT 257 7 "coeffs " }{TEXT 260 1 " " }{TEXT -1 84 "to pick off the c
