bit it. " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
{MPLTEXT 1 0 22 "p4:=a*x^3+b*x^2+c*x+d;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 
