yGF'F(\"#;" }{TEXT -1 3 ",  " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "x^2/36 + y^2/4 = 1" "6#/
,&*&%\"xG\"\"#\"#O!\"\"\"\"\"*&%\"yGF'\"\"%F)F*F*" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 ">
